In Civil Application No. 1277 of 2014 in Writ 
Petition  No. 2550 of 1996, this Court has ordered 
inquiry as regards certain documents, to be made by 
the   Registrar   (Judicial II).     The   learned   Counsel 
appearing for the parties state that infact, the inquiry 
was completed and a report is also submitted. We 
direct the Registrar (Judicial II) to ensure that the 
Registry traces out the files of this petition along 
with the report submitted by the Registrar (Judicial 
II).
Sneha Chavan

week commencing from 21st August 2017.
(SMT. VIBHA KANKANWADI, J.)

Sneha Chavan
